This place has recently opened in Sutton area and earned neighbour's sympathy. The place has such a beautiful ambiance, beating music from all over the world-- catchy Buddha Bar and lounge style, terrace on the second floor where can be book for the private events,smiley staff,and very enthusiastic management that has quality and service in the personal level. After all, food has a delicate and unique tapas experience. The chef adds his culinary taste and executive specials to your visit.
